> I would also like to define a set of "hot" keys, similar to aliases in Diku
> Mud.  Here is the format I use to define these hotkeys on the mud:
> 
> cc cast cure critic
> tr cast tremor
> bl cast bless
> 
> These macros take "arguments" in the sense that I can type "bl Cron" and it
