You can make your own status bar by using the /xtitle  command  of the
tools.tf package.

Example:
/load tools.tf
/xtitle TinyFugue ist nett
Will display the text 'TinyFugue ist nett' in your windows title :)


You can display updated strings to watch your current flags, for example
