The problem is that your patterns match more than you want them to match.
"100%" matches both "10[0-9]+%" and "[1-4]+[0-9]+%", and since they
are fall-through, both triggers are applied, mixing green and red to
produce yellow.

Get rid of each "+" to get the desired effect.  You don't want to match
one-or-more of each of those digits, you want to match exactly one.

