Instead of your /set, use something like:
/test corpses_%{who} := corpses_%{who} + 1

Or:
/test giver_%{who} := {P1}

Or if you want them indexed by numbers use that instead of who.  You
need to assign `who' or just sub in the right variable.  In more recent
tfs you can use the ++ operator instead of adding 1.

