I don't know where you learned to count, but "%;" looks like 2 characters
to me. :)

> /set temp_str=""
> /alias ] /do_expand %{*}
> /def do_expand = \
>         /set temp_str %{*} %;\
>         /while ( $[strchr(temp_str,",")] > -1 ) \
