Check out /help substitute.

e.g.
/def -F -q -p10 -mregexp -t'^A hugh tree walking on big roots' tree_sub =\
  /substitute The Tree %PR

Analysis:
- fall-thru so your other hilites, colours, and triggers will still work.
- Any line starting with "A hugh tree.." will be replaced with "The Tree "
and whatever comes after "roots". (look at /help %PR).

Any lower priority triggers will see "The Tree hits Kalle hard." instead of
the original line, and your colours should work fine, as long as they are of a
lower priority.  I believe partial hilites are lost if they were set from
a higher priority.

